g=A.ai("We used Unity3D networking protocols to create the online garden of improvisations, a collaborative music practice environment. Players were able to invite their friends to their garden encouraged by in-game perks exclusive to online interactions. They could not only share their previous improvisations, and the trees that they created, but also play a concert for them (VOIP) or react to the concert of their friends (emoji messages). Finally, if all of the participants play music together, rain will fall for everyone.  (The project was built for pc, mac, android, google cardboard in android and the web).\n                    ",A.a4(a6,a6,a6,a6,a6,a6),a6,a6)
